OL,3,CNo quick fix for Albert Bridge with
OL,4,Chopes for full repair 'within a year'
OL,6,FAlbert Bridge may not be fully
OL,7,Frepaired for up to a year after a
OL,8,Fcrack was found in part of the iron
OL,9,Fstructure.
OL,11,FThe crossing between Chelsea and
OL,12,FBattersea is closed to traffic and
OL,13,Fbeing monitored by sensors.
OL,15,FKensington and Chelsea Council hope a
OL,16,Ftemporary fix can reopen the bridge
OL,17,Fsooner, but had to prepare for a
OL,18,F"worst case scenario".
