OL,3,CNo quick fix for Albert Bridge with
OL,4,Chopes for full repair 'within a year'
OL,6,F"The early advice we have had
OL,7,Ffollowing initial investigations
OL,8,Fsuggests that we may be able to
OL,9,Fcomplete a permanent fix within a
OL,10,Fyear," said Cllr Johnny Thalassites,
OL,11,Flead member for planning and
OL,12,Fenvironment.
OL,14,F"In the meantime, the investigative
OL,15,Fwork continues. We are working with
OL,16,Fexperts to find out if there are
OL,17,Foptions to employ a temporary fix
OL,18,Fwhich I hope to update on as soon as
OL,19,Fwe have the analysis.
