OL,3,CNo quick fix for Albert Bridge with
OL,4,Chopes for full repair 'within a year'
OL,6,F"Our ambition remains to get this
OL,7,Fbridge open as soon as possible.J"I
OL,8,Fwant to thank motorists for their
OL,9,Fongoing patience, we know it is
OL,10,Ffrustrating.
OL,12,F"But we know for now we have to close
OL,13,Fthe road to avoid the risk of extra
OL,14,Fweight causing further damage that
OL,15,Fcould make repair significantly more
OL,16,Fdifficult, more lengthy and more
OL,17,Fexpensive."
