OL,3,CNo quick fix for Albert Bridge with
OL,4,Chopes for full repair 'within a year'
OL,6,FThe bridge is over 150 years old, used
OL,7,Fby 20,000 cars each day, and serves as
OL,8,Fa key route for residents and
OL,9,Fbusinesses.
OL,11,FTimeline of London's Albert Bridge
OL,13,F1873 - OpeningAlbert Bridge, designed
OL,14,Fby Rowland Mason Ordish and named
OL,15,Fafter Prince Albert, opens as a hybrid
OL,16,Fsuspension and cable-stayed bridge
OL,17,Flinking Chelsea and Battersea.
OL,19,F1884 - Early strengtheningCast-iron
OL,20,Fpiles are added to improve stability
OL,21,Funder increasing traffic.
