OL,3,CNo quick fix for Albert Bridge with
OL,4,Chopes for full repair 'within a year'
OL,6,FFebruary 2026 - Precautionary closure
OL,7,Fto vehiclesKensington and Chelsea
OL,8,FCouncil closes the bridge to motor
OL,9,Ftraffic following a structural
OL,10,Finspection. Pedestrians and cyclists
OL,11,Fcan still cross, while cars are
OL,12,Fdiverted via Chelsea and Battersea
OL,13,Fbridges.
OL,15,FThe council will be keen to avoid a
OL,16,Frepeat of the long-term controversial
OL,17,Fclosure of Hammersmith Bridge which is
OL,18,Fonly open to pedestrians and cyclists.
