OL,6,FThe crossing over the River Thames in
OL,7,Fwest London has been closed to motor
OL,8,Fvehicles since April 2019 after a
OL,9,Fsafety assessment uncovered dangerous
OL,10,Fmicrofractures in the castiron
OL,11,Fpedestals.
OL,13,FThe fractures made the crossing unsafe
OL,14,Ffor cars, buses and heavy traffic.
